</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <fr:p>The <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-004B.xml" title="Reflexive graph" addr="//erct/erct-004B" type="local">reflexive graph</fr:link> structure on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathchoice {\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\textstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{\scriptscriptstyle \prod _{
 \mathopen {}\left \lparen x:A\right \rparen \mathclose {}
}}{Bx}]]></fr:tex> by <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0014.xml" title="Homotopy" addr="//erct/erct-0014" type="local">homotopy</fr:link> and <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0014.xml" title="Homotopy" addr="//erct/erct-0014" type="local">identity homotopies</fr:link> is <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0010.xml" title="Path object" addr="//erct/erct-0010" type="local">univalent</fr:link>.</fr:p>
